{c:'MECH',t:'Gear ratio',d:'GR = Driven \u00f7 Driver teeth. Output RPM = Input \u00f7 GR. 10-tooth driver, 40-tooth driven = 4:1. Speed \u00f74, torque \u00d74.'},
