{c:'MECH',t:'Shaft misalignment types',d:'Parallel: centerlines offset \u2192 2\u00d7 RPM radial vibration. Angular: centerlines meet at angle \u2192 1\u00d7 and 2\u00d7 RPM axial vibration.'},
{c:'MECH',t:'Soft foot rule',d:'Correct BEFORE aligning. Tightening bolts on a machine with soft foot deflects the frame and shifts shaft \u2014 invalidates the alignment.'},
