{c:'HYD',t:'Cylinder force',d:'F = P \u00d7 A. Area = \u03c0 \u00d7 (bore/2)\u00b2. Retraction force = P \u00d7 (bore area \u2212 rod area) \u2014 less because rod reduces piston area.'},
{c:'HYD',t:'Pump types',d:'Gear: simple, fixed displacement, moderate pressure. Vane: quieter. Piston: high pressure, variable displacement \u2014 most demanding applications.'},
