{c:'HYD',t:'Pump cavitation',d:'Whine + low erratic pressure + rapid wear. Causes: clogged inlet strainer, cold fluid, restrictive inlet, low fluid level. Vapor bubbles collapse = erosion.'},
{c:'HYD',t:'Open vs closed center',d:'Open center: pump circulates to tank in neutral (low heat). Closed center: pump flow blocked in neutral \u2014 needs unloading valve.'},
{c:'HYD',t:'Accumulator safety',d:'Stores pressurized fluid under nitrogen. MUST de-pressurize before maintenance. Charged accumulator = pressurized vessel.'},
